                                <img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle;" src="/contentimages/arrow-orange.gif" /> <a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/nsw-pacific-coast-touring-route.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #684c43;">太平洋海岸旅遊路線</span></a><br />
                                <img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle;" src="/contentimages/arrow-orange.gif" /> <a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/qld-pacific-coast.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #684c43;">太平洋海岸旅遊路線</span></a><br />
                                <img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle;" src="/contentimages/arrow-orange.gif" /> <a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/sa-loop.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #684c43;">南澳州環線</span></a></p>
                                </td>
                                <td style="width: 50%;" valign="top">
                                <p><img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle;" src="/contentimages/arrow-orange.gif" /> <a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/nt-natures-way.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #684c43;">大自然之路（Nature’s Way）</span></a><br />
                                <img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle;" src="/contentimages/arrow-orange.gif" /> <a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/wa-savannah.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #684c43;">大草原之路（The Savannah Way）</span></a><br />
                                <img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle;" src="/contentimages/arrow-orange.gif" /> <a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/tas-circle-tas.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #684c43;">環遊塔斯曼尼亞</span></a><br />
                                <img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle;" src="/contentimages/arrow-orange.gif" /> <a href="/zht/explore/itineraries/act-capital-country.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #684c43;">首都與鄉村</span></a></p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                    <br />
                    <p><img alt="" src="/contentimages/about-australias-landscapes-australias-seasons-autumn-zht-title03.jpg" /></p>
                    <table width="92%">
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="width: 50%;" valign="top" colspan="2">
                                <p>挑動您的味蕾，體驗澳洲時裝週的創意精華，乘坐熱氣球飄向遠方或是觀看極速的一級方程式賽車。 </p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
