                                <td style="padding-bottom: 5px; width: 50%; padding-right: 18px;" valign="top">
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/events/melbourne-food-and-wine-festival.xml" target="_self"><img alt="Melbourne Food and Wine Festival" src="/contentimages/explore-events-vic-melbourne-food-and-wine-festival-hl.jpg" /></a></p>
                                <p><a href="/zht/explore/events/melbourne-food-and-wine-festival.xml" target="_self"><span style="color: #684c43; font-size: 12px;"><strong>墨爾本美食美酒節，維多利亞州</strong></span></a></p>
                                </td>
